[Event "Baker Bridge - DONT"]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "1"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "E:A2.KQ83.Q65.AJ94 T7.AJ9742.A82.KQ K5.T.KJT73.87653 QJ98643.65.94.T2"]
[Declarer "N"]
[Contract "2S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "E"]
1NT X pass 2S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 1, chOption: N, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:0, nBasis: 2, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
[BoardVersionToken "a14ec074824365e37e4eaca260556fd856056f558e3eff65aa980c7414133dc6"]
[Category "Competitive Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/dont"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner's double asks you to bid 2\C as a relay bid so he can name his suit.

But you don't want him to bid his 6-card suit, your hand is useless unless \Ss are trumps. So ignore the relay request and bid 2\S. Everybody passes.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
